Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.26,Default,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}6.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.97,Default,Pico,0,0,0,,Srećan put, Vins.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.37,Default,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}5.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.09,Default,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}4.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.06,Default,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}3.
